Package com.java.simonsobstaclecourse.model.obstacle

Interface Obstacle

All Known Implementing Classes:
BottomlessPit, FirePit, SpikePit, Teleporter
public interface Obstacle
An interface representing obstacles in the game. Obstacles define effects to be applied on players and provide unique identifiers.
Author:
Abhishek Wadmare, Lakshay Narula
